# Workflow-generated artifacts that should never be committed back to main:
# - state_sanity.json is regenerated fresh by scripts/check_state_sanity.py
#   on every daily.yml run and uploaded as an artifact. A stale committed
#   copy would be re-read by build_daily_health_report.py and surface dead
#   errors/warnings as fresh issues.
state_sanity.json
daily_stop_go_result.json
